msg: Changed SharedResource to ResourceReference.  ResourceReference does not inherit
from Resource since it is a reference to a resource and not an actual resource now.
Added StaticImageResourceReference to make it easy to create references to static
image resources.  See the Tree class for an example usage.  SharedResourceLink
